{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":110500,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1105_00_01","textHome":"我是从魔法报告的世界来的菲莉希亚。@虽然不知道跟这边世界的有什么区别……@总之打倒魔女是一样的吧？@魔女出现的话我就直接打飞它，记得叫我来！@那，没事的话先摸了，别的就拜托你了——"}],"deleteArmatureList":[1]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"id":110500,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":110500,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_012.exp.json","id":110500,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":110500,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":110500,"motion":100}]}],"group_10":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":110500,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1105_00_17","textHome":"八千代说要好好选记忆结晶装上，@但是不知道哪个比较好啊。@是星越多越好么？"}],"deleteArmatureList":[1]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_012.exp.json","id":110500}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":110500,"motion":100}]}],"group_11":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":110500,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1105_00_18","textHome":"好嘞！最强的我自己完成了！@关于记忆结晶，只要想好技能的搭配，@就能变强了。还好问了鹤乃。"}],"deleteArmatureList":[1]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":110500,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_012.exp.json","id":110500,"motion":100}]}],"group_12":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_012.exp.json","id":110500,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1105_00_19","textHome":"这样就能吃得更多了！"}],"deleteArmatureList":[1]}],"group_13":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":110500,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1105_00_20","textHome":"看到了我以外的我自己吗，@是大奖赛那时的家伙吗？"}],"deleteArmatureList":[1]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":110500}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":110500,"motion":300}]}],"group_14":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":110500,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1105_00_21","textHome":"有过菲莉希亚大奖赛的，@不知道为什么有着三个我自己！@当然最后优胜的是你面前这个！！"}],"deleteArmatureList":[1]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":110500,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_012.exp.json","id":110500,"motion":100}]}],"group_15":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":110500,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1105_00_22","textHome":"大奖赛其中一个我，是靠玛吉斯的深度教育，@变成了能够执行详细的自动战斗指令的家伙。@啊，酱油配水团好像很好吃啊。@哎，给咱做点肉吃呗。"}],"deleteArmatureList":[1]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.9,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":110500}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":110500}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":110500,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_012.exp.json","id":110500,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":110500,"motion":200}]}],"group_16":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":110500,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1105_00_23","textHome":"另一个我呢，是在东区斯巴达式的教育下，@拥有了不用动画就能放出Magia的敏捷。@咱自己的话，有肉吃就好啦。@对啦，就当庆祝成长，去吃烤肉吧！"}],"deleteArmatureList":[1]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.8,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":110500}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.7,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":110500}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.4,"chara":[{"id":110500,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_012.exp.json","id":110500}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"id":110500,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":110500,"motion":100}]}],"group_17":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_063.exp.json","id":110500,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1105_00_24","textHome":"啊……好无聊……啊？来了吗……@要是有魔女出现就告诉我。@没事的话……我就和地板融为一体了……"}],"deleteArmatureList":[1]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":110500}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":110500,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_063.exp.json","id":110500}]}],"group_18":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":110500,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1105_00_25","textHome":"呼——呜，嗯……我还困着呢……@嗷嗷嗷！？……呜……别摇了……@再摇也不会起来的……呼……"}],"deleteArmatureList":[1]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":110500}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"effect":"shake","face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":110500,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":110500,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":10.6,"chara":[{"id":110500,"motion":0}]}],"group_19":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_012.exp.json","id":110500,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1105_00_26","textHome":"吃完午饭……就要午睡啦！@最幸福的时光！所以我睡了！@别的事就交给你啦……咕咕……"}],"deleteArmatureList":[1]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":110500,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":110500,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":8.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":110500}]}],"group_2":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":110500,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1105_00_02","textHome":"嗯，啊？这是哪里？@嗯？什么啊八千代，要说啥悄悄话？@嗯——这样说就行了吗？@咱是来自魔法报告世界的菲莉希亚，@请多关照啦！"}],"deleteArmatureList":[1]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":110500,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":110500,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.7,"chara":[{"id":110500,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":110500,"motion":200}]}],"group_20":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":110500,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1105_00_27","textHome":"嘿咻，嘿咻……@什么啊，我在万万岁帮工有什么好意外的？@结束了有炒饭吃的呀。"}],"deleteArmatureList":[1]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":110500,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_012.exp.json","id":110500,"motion":200}]}],"group_21":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":110500,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1105_00_28","textHome":"呜……嗯……哈！什么啊，是梦啊。@偶尔会梦见咯咯咯笑的女人@和被拿着鞭子的女人吊起来的梦……"}],"deleteArmatureList":[1]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":110500,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_032.exp.json","id":110500,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":110500,"motion":300}]}],"group_22":[{"armatureList":[{"animation":["action"],"armatureId":1,"filePath":"resource/image_native/effect/story/general/3007_papa_butterfly.ExportJson","zOrder":"messageBack"}],"autoTurnFirst":7.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_063.exp.json","id":110500,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1105_00_29","textHome":"啊———————————"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_053.exp.json","id":110500,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_063.exp.json","id":110500,"motion":1}]}],"group_23":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_012.exp.json","id":110500,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1105_00_30","textHome":"锵！魔女出现了！@好嘞，交给我吧！打爆它！ "}],"deleteArmatureList":[1]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"id":110500,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":110500,"motion":200}]}],"group_24":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_053.exp.json","id":110500,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1105_00_31","textHome":"第一次来的时候，把御魂当成镜之魔女，@一锤子敲进地里了……"}],"deleteArmatureList":[1]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.4,"chara":[{"id":110500,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":110500,"motion":300}]}],"group_25":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_012.exp.json","id":110500,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1105_00_32","textHome":"好多的魔法少女！@哎？为什么有好几个长得一样的……@尤其是那俩粉毛，总共有几个啊？"}],"deleteArmatureList":[1]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":110500,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":110500,"motion":0}]}],"group_26":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":110500,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1105_00_33","textHome":"想升星？星星多了能干啥啊？@又不能吃吧？所以说，多来点肉啊！肉！"}],"deleteArmatureList":[1]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.3,"chara":[{"id":110500,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_012.exp.json","id":110500,"motion":200}]}],"group_27":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":110500,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1105_00_34","textHome":"嘎——鬼来了！怎样！吓不吓人？@咱的角像鬼嘛。所以，就在撒豆子里扮鬼了。@彩羽给我撒了好多豆子。"}],"deleteArmatureList":[1]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_012.exp.json","id":110500,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":110500,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":110500}]}],"group_28":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_063.exp.json","id":110500,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1105_00_35","textHome":"「无脑就是干」「不放Magia」@「蔬菜也要吃」？@这都啥玩儿啊？看不懂。@战斗的话抡锤子不就好了嘛！"}],"deleteArmatureList":[1]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":110500,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":110500,"moti